OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association, he
OL,8,Fsaid he was "doing fine".
OL,10,FAt the moment, he said that his cancer
OL,11,Fis not stopping him from doing
OL,12,Fanything that he loves.
OL,14,F"I'm doing fine, thanks," Sir Chris
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"The Tour de 4 is the main focus for
OL,18,Fme the next few months."
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@XO]vD@AOUvD@YO]yD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
