FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,FThe event is a charity bike ride for
OL,8,Fpeople affected by cancer, which is
OL,9,Ftaking place in Glasgow in September.
OL,11,FIt raised more than #3.1 million in
OL,12,Fits inaugural year in 2025, and it
OL,13,Fwill support five major UK cancer
OL,14,Fcharities as well as challenge
OL,15,Fperceptions of people living with
OL,16,Fstage four cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,F"It's trying to demonstrate, rather
OL,8,Fthan just talking about it, that all
OL,9,Fthese people who are in a similar
OL,10,Fsituation to me ` living with stage
OL,11,Ffour cancer ` that there's plenty of
OL,12,Flife left in us, and we're determined
OL,13,Fto make the most of it, and not have
OL,14,Fcancer define who you are," Sir Chris
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe previously said the Tour de 4 event
OL,18,Fhas become a driving force for him
OL,19,Ffollowing his terminal cancer
OL,20,Fdiagnosis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,F"You don't have to be facing a stage
OL,8,Ffour cancer diagnosis to have tough
OL,9,Fmoments," Sir Chris said.
OL,11,F"I guess for me and for my family, the
OL,12,Fthing that we've tried to do is to not
OL,13,Flook too far ahead and to still have
OL,14,Fplans for the future and still have
OL,15,Fgoals and aims and things to look
OL,16,Fforward to."
OL,18,FSpeaking about holding on to hope, he
OL,19,Fsaid it is about appreciating the
OL,20,Fsmall things and making the most out
OL,21,Fof the present.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]sD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,F"Don't forget to enjoy the moment and
OL,8,Fdon't forget to appreciate the
OL,9,Fpresent, because it passes you by very
OL,10,Feasily," the Olympian said.
OL,12,F"You're always on to the next thing
OL,13,Fand focused on what's next, and you
OL,14,Fcan miss out on the nice stuff around
OL,15,Fyou ` and it's not necessarily the big
OL,16,Fthings."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@HO]tD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,FHe continued: "We have big targets and
OL,8,Fbig events to look forward to, of
OL,9,Fcourse, but I think it's also
OL,10,Fappreciating the small things that
OL,11,Fhelps you to stay grounded, and to
OL,12,Fmake the most out of the present
OL,13,Fmoment."
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
