CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,FCircling back to the Tour de 4, Sir
OL,8,FChris said the main two rides for the
OL,9,Fevent in September are already sold
OL,10,Fout, but he said there are still
OL,11,Fplaces for the static bikes in the
OL,12,Ftrack centre and for the family loop,
OL,13,Fwhich is a 1k loop inside the
OL,14,Fvelodrome complex.
OL,16,FHe said people can still be part of
OL,17,Fthe event by donating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780876973
OL,3,CChris Hoy on redefining late-stage
OL,4,Ccancer: 'There's plenty of life left
OL,5,Cin us'
OL,7,F"It really is going to be a big
OL,8,Fchallenge to try and beat the #3.1
OL,9,Fmillion target that we achieved from
OL,10,Flast year," Sir Chris said.
OL,12,F"Every single pound will go towards
OL,13,Fimproving people's lives, living with
OL,14,Fcancer, and for the future as well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]tD@AOUvD@dO]
